'''Valentinos Sielis''' (born 1 March 1990), is a [[Cyprus|Cypriot]] [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (association football)#Wing-back|Left back]] for [[Cyprus First Division]] club [[Anorthosis Famagusta FC]]. Sielis is considered one of the best footballers in the Cyprus. He awarded with the award of the best youth player in Cyprus in May 2012.<ref name="best youth">[http://anorthosinews.blogspot.com/2012/05/blog-post_8427.html <U+039A><U+03B1><U+03BB><U+03C5><U+03C4><U+03B5><U+03C1><U+03BF><U+03C2> <U+03BD><U+03B5><U+03BF><U+03C2> <U+03C0><U+03BF><U+03B4><U+03BF><U+03C3><U+03C6><U+03B1><U+03B9><U+03C1><U+03B9><U+03C3><U+03C4><U+03B7><U+03C2> <U+03BF> <U+03A3><U+03B9><U+03B5><U+03BB><U+03B7><U+03C2>], anorthosinews.blogspot.com, Retrieved 08 May 2012</ref> Sielis is a [[Cyprus|Cypriot]] [[Cyprus national football team|international]] and made his debut on 9 February 2011, against [[Romania national football team]] for the [[CytaVision]] Cyprus Tournament 2011.<ref name="captain u21"></ref>

==Early life==

Sielis was born in [[Paphos]], a town of [[Cyprus]], the middle child of his family, Valentinos have two brothers the older brother [[Giorgos Sielis]] a football player of [[AEK Kouklia F.C.|AEK Kouklia]] and Christos Sielis the youngest brother of valentinos who current plays for Youth team of [[Arsenal|Arsenal Elite]].

==Club career==

===Early career===
Sielis began his career in England first in Arsenal F.C. U12, Tottenham F.C U13, the first professional team for [[Doncaster Rovers F.C.]],<ref>{{cite news | year=2008 |url=http://www.teamtalk.com/doncaster-rovers/player-profile/102160/Valentinos-Sielis| title=Sielis in Doncaster | publisher=teamtalk.com}}</ref> Sielis signed with local club of [[ENTHOI Lakatamia FC|Enosis Neon Thoi Lakatamia FC]], and after a grate season he moved to [[Anorthosis Famagusta FC|Anorthosis Famagusta]]

===Anorthosis Famagusta===
Valentinos Sielis joined to Anorthosis at 15 June, 2009 from [[ENTHOI Lakatamia FC|Enosis Neon Thoi Lakatamia FC]] as a [[Free agent]].

Sielis made his team debut as 30th-minute substitute in a 0-3 away victory over [[Othellos Athienou F.C.]] for [[Cypriot Cup 2009<U+2013>10|Cypriot Cup]] on 23 September 2009.<ref>[http://newsite.kathimerini.com.cy/index.php?pageaction=kat&modid=1&artid=6260&show=Y ''<U+039A><U+03B1><U+03B8><U+03AC><U+03C1><U+03B9><U+03C3><U+03B5>'' <U+03C4><U+03B7><U+03BD> <U+03C0><U+03C1><U+03CC><U+03BA><U+03C1><U+03B9><U+03C3><U+03B7> <U+03B7> <U+0391><U+03BD><U+03CC><U+03C1><U+03B8><U+03C9><U+03C3><U+03B7>, 3-0 <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03BD> <U+039F><U+03B8><U+03AD><U+03BB><U+03BB><U+03BF>], kathimerini.com.cy, Retrieved 23 September 2009</ref> he play as a first time in a European competition on the starting squad in a 1-2 home defeat from [[PFC CSKA Moscow|CSKA Moscow]] in [[Antonis Papadopoulos Stadium]] for the [[2010<U+2013>11 UEFA Europa League|UEFA Europa League]] 4th qualifying round.<ref>[http://www.sigmalive.com/sports/football/cyprus/a%20league/298841 <U+0391><U+03BD><U+03CC><U+03C1><U+03B8><U+03C9><U+03C3><U+03B7>-<U+03A4><U+03A3><U+03A3><U+039A><U+0391> 1-2 <U+0395> <U+03CC><U+03C7><U+03B9> <U+03BA><U+03B9>' <U+03AD><U+03C4><U+03C3><U+03B9> ..], sigmalive.com. Retrieved 26 August 2010</ref> he made his debut as 72th-minute in [[2010<U+2013>11 Cypriot First Division|Cypus first division]] in a 2-1 home victory over [[Olympiakos Nicosia]].<ref>[http://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/en/anorthosis-famagusta-olympiakos-nicosia/index/spielbericht_1050708.html Anorthosisi - Olympiakos: 2-1 match analysis], transfermarkt.co.uk, Retrieved 25 September 2014</ref> At the end of the season he played for 18 matches, 10 of them as a substitution, with 875 minutes of total playing time. On 8 May 2011, Sielis played for a first time in a Derby on the basic squad in a 1-0 away defeat from [[Omonia Nicosia]].<ref>[http://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/en/omonia-nikosia-anorthosis-famagusta/index/spielbericht_1050753.html Omonia - Anorthosis: 1-0 match analysis], transfermarkt.co.uk, Retrieved 08 May 2011</ref> For the season 2011-12, during the period with coach [[Stanimir Stoilov]], Sielis was a basic player of Anorthosis in the [[Europa League 2011-12|European competitions]] with 3 appearance in 4 matches, all as a substitution. After the arrival of [[Ronny Levy]], Sielis played 4 times, once on the basic squad against [[Olympiakos Nicosia]].<ref>[http://www.anorthosis.com/players/2/60 Valentinos Sielis Appearance with Anorthosis]</ref> For the season 2012-13, Sielis, Began the season as the second left back of the team. After the announchment that [[William Boaventura]] end his career,<ref>[http://www.onsports.gr/Podosfairo/Eyrwph/Kypros/item/253863-Kremaei-ta-papoytsia-toy-o-Mpoabentoyra <U+00AB><U+039A><U+03C1><U+03B5><U+03BC><U+03AC><U+03B5><U+03B9><U+00BB> <U+03C4><U+03B1> <U+03C0><U+03B1><U+03C0><U+03BF><U+03CD><U+03C4><U+03C3><U+03B9><U+03B1> <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03C5> <U+03BF> <U+039C><U+03C0><U+03BF><U+03B1><U+03B2><U+03B5><U+03BD><U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03CD><U+03C1><U+03B1>;], onsports.gr, Retrieved 23 September 2012</ref> Siels became the main left back of the team. From 8th until 19th match day Sielis starts all the matches in the basic lineup.<ref>[http://www.transfermarkt.co.uk/en/valentinos-sielis/leistungsdaten/spieler_123627_2012.html Valentinos Sielis Appearance 2013-14]</ref> On March 2013, Sielis had a serious injury and he made a surgery as a result to lost all the other matches until the end of the season.<ref>[http://www.sigmalive.com/sports/football/cyprus/a-league/34549 <U+03A7><U+03B5><U+03B9><U+03C1><U+03BF><U+03C5><U+03C1><U+03B3><U+03AE><U+03B8><U+03B7><U+03BA><U+03B5> <U+03BC><U+03B5> <U+03B5><U+03C0><U+03B9><U+03C4><U+03C5><U+03C7><U+03AF><U+03B1> <U+03BF> <U+03A3><U+03B9><U+03AD><U+03BB><U+03B7><U+03C2>], sigmalive.com, Retrieved 11 March 2013</ref>

==Outside football==
===Volunteering===
Valentinos Sielis is particularly sensitive to issues related to helping our fellowmen. It is amazing that in the transmission of reckoning [[AEL Limassol]] - [[Anorthosis Famagusta FC|Anorthosis]] from [[CytaVision]], Savvas Kosiaris, some time before the accident with [[Andrija Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>|Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>]] said that Sielis is compatible donor bone marrow and has helped a fellow human to stay alive.<ref name="heroic act">[http://sentragoal.philenews.com/article.asp?catid=19170&subid=2&pubid=129710851 <U+0398><U+03B1><U+03C5><U+03BC><U+03B1><U+03C3><U+03BC><U+03CC><U+03C2> <U+03B3><U+03B9><U+03B1> <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03BD> <U+03A3><U+03B9><U+03AD><U+03BB><U+03B7> <U+03C0><U+03BF><U+03C5> <U+03B2><U+03BF><U+03AE><U+03B8><U+03B7><U+03C3><U+03B5> <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03BD> <U+039A><U+03B1><U+03BB><U+03BF><U+03C5><U+03BD><U+03C4><U+03B6><U+03AD><U+03C1><U+03BF><U+03B2><U+03B9><U+03C4><U+03C2>], sentragoal.philenews.com, Retrieved 26 April 2014</ref>

===Heroic act - Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107> serious injury===
At 26 April 2014, the striker of [[AEL Limassol]], [[Andrija Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>]] claimed the ball with [[Paulo Jorge Soares Gomes|Paulo Jorge]] and seemed to hit the head of his opponent, with [[Andrija Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>|Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>]] to fall to the ground unconscious. <U+03A4>he sportswriter of Cytavision who was in stage, said that [[Andrija Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>|Kalu<U+0111>erovi<U+0107>]] swallowed his tongue and Sielis he brought him back, with the Cypriot gave them first aid.<ref name="heroic act"></ref><ref>[http://www.kerkida.net/articles/a-katigoria/eidiseis/36493-tipota-allo-den-ehei-simasia-o-sielis-gia-tin-kinisi-toy "<U+03A4><U+03AF><U+03C0><U+03BF><U+03C4><U+03B1> <U+03AC><U+03BB><U+03BB><U+03BF> <U+03B4><U+03B5><U+03BD> <U+03AD><U+03C7><U+03B5><U+03B9> <U+03C3><U+03B7><U+03BC><U+03B1><U+03C3><U+03AF><U+03B1>" (O <U+03A3><U+03B9><U+03AD><U+03BB><U+03B7><U+03C2> <U+03B3><U+03B9><U+03B1> <U+03C4><U+03B7><U+03BD> <U+03BA><U+03AF><U+03BD><U+03B7><U+03C3><U+03AE> <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03C5>)], kerkida.net, Retrieved 26 April 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.kerkida.net/articles/a-katigoria/eidiseis/ael/36486-o-fetinos-protathlitis <U+039F> <U+03C6><U+03B5><U+03C4><U+03B9><U+03BD><U+03CC><U+03C2>... <U+03C0><U+03C1><U+03C9><U+03C4><U+03B1><U+03B8><U+03BB><U+03B7><U+03C4><U+03AE><U+03C2>], kerkida.net, Retrieved 26 April 2014</ref><ref>[http://www.24sports.com.cy/index.php?pageaction=kat&modid=1&artid=88887 <U+03A7><U+03AF><U+03BB><U+03B9><U+03B1> <U+03BC><U+03C0><U+03C1><U+03AC><U+03B2><U+03BF> <U+03C3><U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03BD> <U+03A3><U+03B9><U+03AD><U+03BB><U+03B7> <U+03B3><U+03B9><U+03B1> <U+03C4><U+03BF> <U+03B8><U+03AC><U+03C1><U+03C1><U+03BF><U+03C2> <U+03C4><U+03BF><U+03C5>], 24sports.com.cy, Retrieved 26 April 2014</ref>

